responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "7F0573D048D9382587972A9765C03B83", "While gone Godling, visions reached me, brought by the ancestors. Their voices carried on winds that whispered through the canyon, clear and certain. They revealed a path unseen, one that calls for trust. The Horn of the Great Herd, sacred to my future, must pass for a time. This is not a loss, but an offering, a gift entrusted to the future that lies beyond our sight.")
